    {
      "id": "PopularPost144926",
      "post_content": "This card teaches that '1 mana = 1 damage' is about right in the middle of the curve for red, any less is a bad card, any more is a good one. Lightning Bolt unfortunately destroys this lesson, by making greedy Spike n00bs think '1 mana = 3 damage and any less is a bad card', which if it were true would warp the game faster than the existence of Goku warped power level judgement in DBZ-\n  \nremember when being 'OVER NINE THOUSAND' was a big deal? a few dozen episodes later, and 10 MILLION was considered 'meh- you might be worth my time'. Here's hoping that doesn't happen to Magic.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost144926\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This card teaches that '1 mana = 1 damage' is about right in the middle of the curve for red, any less is a bad card, any more is a good one.  Lightning Bolt unfortunately destroys this lesson, by making greedy Spike n00bs think '1 mana = 3 damage and any less is a bad card', which if it were true would warp the game faster than the existence of Goku warped power level judgement in DBZ- \r<br/>remember when being 'OVER NINE THOUSAND' was a big deal? a few dozen episodes later, and 10 MILLION was considered 'meh- you might be worth my time'.  Here's hoping that doesn't happen to Magic.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '144926'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (3/18/2011 11:24:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../I